。经过过去一年左右的流血、汗水和泪水，这证明了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/uk-venues-react-to-reopening-today-for-socially-distanced-gigs-we-are-back-2942261">音乐场馆信托基金和我们所在的各地音乐场馆付出的巨大努力</a>。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-fat-white-familys-emotive-new-single-religion-for-one-3557799">聆听 Fat White Family 情感丰富的新单曲“Religion For One”的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
